caid.Rd

Medicaid Endpoint

Medicaid Endpoint Group

Medicaid Temporal Endpoint

Usage

caid_endpoint(alias)

caid_group(alias)

caid_temporal(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <caid_endpoint> object.

An S7 <caid_group> object.

An S7 <caid_temporal> object.
